#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.50"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.50:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.50:0.2"
msgid "5. Dhammikavagga"
msgstr "5. About Dhammika"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.50:0.3"
msgid "50. Indriyasaṃvarasutta"
msgstr "50. Sense Restraint"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.360"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.50:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Indriyasaṃvare, bhikkhave, asati indriyasaṃvaravipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti "
"sīlaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when there is no sense restraint, one who lacks sense restraint "
"has destroyed a vital condition for ethical conduct."

msgctxt "an6.50:1.2"
msgid "sīle asati sīlavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti sammāsamādhi;"
msgstr ""
"When there is no ethical conduct, one who lacks ethics has destroyed a vital "
"condition for right immersion."

msgctxt "an6.50:1.3"
msgid ""
"sammāsamādhimhi asati sammāsamādhivipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti "
"yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"When there is no right immersion, one who lacks right immersion has "
"destroyed a vital condition for true knowledge and vision."

msgctxt "an6.50:1.4"
msgid ""
"yathābhūtañāṇadassane asati yathābhūtañāṇadassanavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti "
"nibbidāvirāgo;"
msgstr ""
"When there is no true knowledge and vision, one who lacks true knowledge and "
"vision has destroyed a vital condition for disillusionment and dispassion."

msgctxt "an6.50:1.5"
msgid ""
"nibbidāvirāge asati nibbidāvirāgavipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti "
"vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"When there is no disillusionment and dispassion, one who lacks "
"disillusionment and dispassion has destroyed a vital condition for knowledge "
"and vision of freedom."

msgctxt "an6.50:1.6"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, rukkho sākhāpalāsavipanno."
msgstr "Suppose there was a tree that lacked branches and foliage."

msgctxt "an6.50:1.7"
msgid ""
"Tassa papaṭikāpi na pāripūriṃ gacchati, tacopi na pāripūriṃ gacchati, "
"pheggupi na pāripūriṃ gacchati, sāropi na pāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr "Its shoots, bark, softwood, and heartwood would not grow to fullness."

msgctxt "an6.50:1.8"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, indriyasaṃvare asati indriyasaṃvaravipannassa "
"hatūpanisaṃ hoti sīlaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when there is no sense restraint, one who lacks sense "
"restraint has destroyed a vital condition for ethical conduct. …"

msgctxt "an6.50:1.9"
msgid "vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"One who lacks disillusionment and dispassion has destroyed a vital condition "
"for knowledge and vision of freedom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.50:2.1"
msgid ""
"Indriyasaṃvare, bhikkhave, sati indriyasaṃvarasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ "
"hoti sīlaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"When there is sense restraint, one who has sense restraint has fulfilled a "
"vital condition for ethical conduct."

msgctxt "an6.50:2.2"
msgid "sīle sati sīlasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti sammāsamādhi;"
msgstr ""
"When there is ethical conduct, one who has fulfilled ethical conduct has "
"fulfilled a vital condition for right immersion."

msgctxt "an6.50:2.3"
msgid ""
"sammāsamādhimhi sati sammāsamādhisampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti "
"yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"When there is right immersion, one who has fulfilled right immersion has "
"fulfilled a vital condition for true knowledge and vision."

msgctxt "an6.50:2.4"
msgid ""
"yathābhūtañāṇadassane sati yathābhūtañāṇadassanasampannassa upanisasampanno "
"hoti nibbidāvirāgo;"
msgstr ""
"When there is true knowledge and vision, one who has fulfilled true "
"knowledge and vision has fulfilled a vital condition for disillusionment and "
"dispassion."

msgctxt "an6.50:2.5"
msgid ""
"nibbidāvirāge sati nibbidāvirāgasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti "
"vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"When there is disillusionment and dispassion, one who has fulfilled "
"disillusionment and dispassion has fulfilled a vital condition for knowledge "
"and vision of freedom."

msgctxt "an6.50:2.6"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, rukkho sākhāpalāsasampanno. Tassa papaṭikāpi "
"pāripūriṃ gacchati, tacopi pāripūriṃ gacchati, pheggupi pāripūriṃ gacchati, "
"sāropi pāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a tree that was complete with branches and foliage. Its "
"shoots, bark, softwood, and heartwood would all grow to fullness."

msgctxt "an6.50:2.7"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, indriyasaṃvare sati indriyasaṃvarasampannassa "
"upanisasampannaṃ hoti sīlaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when there is sense restraint, one who has fulfilled sense "
"restraint has fulfilled a vital condition for ethical conduct. …"

msgctxt "an6.50:2.8"
msgid "vimuttiñāṇadassanan”ti."
msgstr ""
"One who has fulfilled disillusionment and dispassion has fulfilled a vital "
"condition for knowledge and vision of freedom.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.50:2.9"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
